Vclk (clk 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[ 0n 0 4.9n 0 5.0n 0.9 5.5n 0.9 5.6n 0 14.9n 0 15.0n 0.9 15.5n 0.9 15.6n 0 24.9n 0 25.0n 0.9 25.5n 0.9 25.6n 0 34.9n 0 35.0n 0.9 35.5n 0.9 35.6n 0 44.9n 0 45.0n 0.9 45.5n 0.9 45.6n 0 64.9n 0 65.0n 0.9 65.5n 0.9 65.6n 0 75n 0 ]

